							</div>
													<div class="Grid Grid--with-gutter d:f@md p-b:4">
								<div class="Grid__cell d:f h:full m-b:.5 m-b:0@md w:12"></div>

								<div class="Grid__cell flx-s:1 p-r:4">
									<p>
											CA: I mean, this is another pic
											of your other two kids, Rory and Phoebe,
											along with Paul Farmer.
											Bringing up three children
											when you&#39;re the world&#39;s richest family
