											I guess there&#39;s a long version
and a short version of that.
											We&#39;ve got time for the short version.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
													<div class="Grid Grid--with-gutter d:f@md p-b:4">
								<div class="Grid__cell d:f h:full m-b:.5 m-b:0@md w:12"></div>

								<div class="Grid__cell flx-s:1 p-r:4">
									<p>
											BG: All right. Well, Warren was a close friend,
											and he was going to have his wife Suzie
											give it all away.
